Sara Rasmussen (amụrụ ya n'afọ 1990) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị America si Alaska
Onye Republican, ọ bụ onye otu Alaska House of Representatives, na-anọchite anya District 22.
Rasmussen nwere ọ tutu ụlọ na ụlọ
Ọ rụkwara ọrụ na Sand Lake Community Council.
Rasmussen meriri onye ya nọ n'ọkwa Jason Grenn na ntuli aka n'afọ  2018.
